<emphasis id="B919EACFEFCB3AAFFD50FD3DFCC6FCC9" box="[661,771,755,776]" italics="true" pageId="154" pageNumber="155">Periproctia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Firstendopodal segment of mandible armed with 4 or 5 setae; legs 1–4 with 3-segmented endopod ........................ ...................................................................... 
<taxonomicName id="4C6D4D5EEFCB3AAFFDB8FC97FCC7FCAF" authorityName="Buchholz" authorityYear="1869" box="[637,770,857,878]" class="Maxillopoda" family="Notodelphyidae" genus="Goniodelphys" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cyclopoida" pageId="154" pageNumber="155" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B919EACFEFCB3AAFFDB8FC97FCC7FCAF" box="[637,770,857,878]" italics="true" pageId="154" pageNumber="155">Goniodelphys</emphasis>
